This project intend to test some basic features of apache cassandra, like:
	- write to a simple column family
	- read from a simple column family
	- updates a specific column value
	- increment and decrement distributed counters
	- get counter value

2011-10-14 - New support for cassandra: 0.8.x

Tested with cassandra version: 0.8.7

This project uses:

Apache Cassandra:
http://cassandra.apache.org/

The Hector API a high level cassandra client:
https://github.com/rantav/hector

